you can set an higher mass for the mun tho ![;)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif)

    @Kopernicus:AFTER[Kopernicus]{    @Body[Mun]    {        @Properties        {            mass = something_appropriate        }    }}

PS: [**KSP-AVC**](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/79745) compatibility added to the mod

